<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="medicine-n">medicine <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'medsn,'medɪsn/    美 /'medsn,'medɪsn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>药 (物)；内服药：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>took medicine</strong> twice a day. 
我一天服药两次。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Laughter is the best medicine. 
欢笑是副良药。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>医学；医术：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My daughter has decided to study medicine. 
我女儿决定学医。</p><footer>外研② – 1</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Modern m<strong><em>_</em></strong>_ has cured many diseases that used to kill many people.  （2005 浙江）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. medicine  </p></div>